### 2. Tracking All Methods in a Class

```python
import time
from flexprofiler import track_all, stats

@track_all()  # Use @track_all() decorator to profile all methods in the class
class Foo:
    def example_method(self):
        self.another_method()
        time.sleep(0.1)
    def another_method(self):
        time.sleep(0.2)

Foo().example_method()
Foo().another_method()

stats()
```

output:
