### 4. Track All lines in a function

```python
import time
from flexprofiler import track, stats

@track(lines=True)
def bar(n):
    total = 0
    for i in range(n):
        total += i
        if i % 2 == 0:
            time.sleep(0.001)
        else:
            time.sleep(0.0005)
    return total

@track()
def foo():
    for _ in range(3):
        bar(50)
```

